commit.message: Add test script for the issue.

Fix buffer overflow in eth_switch.

ETHSW_MAX_PKT_SIZE is set to 2048 and packet lengths are not checked at all.
There is a buffer overflow when dot1q code adds a tag using a buffer based on that size.

Fixes #105
Simplify SO_REUSEADDR warnings and add bind/listen errors.
